            {
                "comment": "Professor Yin is a humorous and fun professor that takes a little warming up to. He teaches from the book and can explain even the most difficult concepts. However, he is teaching an incredibly difficult subject and makes no effort to attempting to make it more understandable. Put in the time and you will succeed!",
